OL,5,G```FWORLD JUNIOR CHAMPIONSHIPSG````````
OL,7,GEngland'sFHarriet Hunt,G18, from       
OL,8,GOxford, with a superb score ofC10\/13, 
OL,9,Ghas won the Womens World Junior        
OL,10,Gchampionships, held in Zagan, Poland.  
OL,12,GRoundsC8-13Gproved to be the decisive  
OL,13,Gturning point forFHarrietGin the       
OL,14,Gtournament - she scored a staggering   
OL,15,C5\/6!                                  
OL,17,GScotland'sFHeather LangGhad a final    
OL,18,Gscore ofC5/13.                         
