OL,5,G```FLADIES vs VETERANSG````````````````
OL,7,GAge and guile defeated youth and       
OL,8,Ginnocence as theFVeteransGbeat the     
OL,9,FLadiesGby a score ofC27-23,Gin the     
OL,10,GHostdance Tournament in Copenhagen.    
OL,12,GTheFVeteransGhave now equalised the    
OL,13,Gscores in this novel annual match -    
OL,14,Gnamed after dances from the host       
OL,15,Gcountries - toC3-3,Gthough they now    
OL,16,Ghold a slender over-all score ofC183\- 
OL,17,C182\.                                  
